Uploader - CakePHP Plugin
******************************

Requirements
============

	* CakePHP 1.2
	* PHP 5.2.x
	* Being Awesome

Installation
============

	Documentation:
		* http://www.milesj.me/resources/script/uploader-plugin

	Quick Installation:
		* Clone the repo into a folder called "uploader" within your CakePHP's plugins directory.
		* Add the uploader to the components: public $components = array('Uploader.Uploader');
		* Or use the behaviors: public $actsAs = array('Uploader.Attachment', 'Uploader.FileValidation');
